const faqs = [
  { q: 'Do you handle urgent no-cool AC repair?', a: 'Yes. Call (813) 395-2324 and we will tell you the earliest available appointment before dispatch. During heat waves we prioritize homes without working cooling, especially when safety is a concern.' },
  { q: 'How fast can you get to my house for emergency AC repair?', a: 'Response depends on the day, weather, route load, and parts needed. Our team dispatches from Wesley Chapel and gives a realistic ETA before sending a technician. We are not a 24/7 call center, we are a local crew, so we give you an honest arrival window, not a fake promise.' },
  { q: 'What counts as an AC emergency?', a: 'No cooling during summer heat (especially with infants, elderly residents, or pets), water leaks actively damaging flooring or drywall, electrical smells or smoke from the air handler, or a completely dead system in a storm-damaged home.' },
  { q: 'How much does emergency AC repair cost in Tampa?', a: 'Pricing depends on the diagnosis and the failed part. We quote the full flat-rate number before any work, with no meter-running hourly billing. If the repair is large, we offer 0% financing through Synchrony so a hot house never has to wait on a paycheck.' },
